---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import fisioterapeutaBarcelona from '../../../assets/fisioterapeuta-barcelona.png'
import WhatsAppButton from '../../WhatsAppButton.astro'
---

<section class='relative overflow-hidden py-24 sm:py-32'>

  <!-- Dot-grid texture -->
  <div
    class='pointer-events-none absolute inset-0'
    aria-hidden='true'
    style='background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(52,101,109,0.07) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 28px 28px;'
  ></div>

  <!-- Ghost watermark -->
  <div
    class='pointer-events-none absolute -right-6 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 select-none leading-none'
    aria-hidden='true'
    style='font-family: "Titan One", cursive; font-size: clamp(12rem, 24vw, 20rem); color: rgba(52,101,109,0.06); line-height: 1; white-space: nowrap;'
  >
    WEB
  </div>

  <!-- Radial ambient glow -->
  <div
    class='pointer-events-none absolute -top-40 -left-40 w-[600px] h-[600px] rounded-full'
    aria-hidden='true'
    style='background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(52,101,109,0.04) 0%, transparent 65%);'
  ></div>

  <!-- Top/bottom hairlines -->
  <div class='pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-teal/15 to-transparent' aria-hidden='true'></div>
  <div class='pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-teal/15 to-transparent' aria-hidden='true'></div>

  <div class='mx-auto max-w-[1280px] px-5'>
    <div class='mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:max-w-none lg:grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_480px] lg:gap-16 xl:gap-24 items-center'>

      <!-- LEFT: Plain explanation -->
      <div>

        <!-- Eyebrow -->
        <div data-animate class='flex items-center gap-3 mb-8'>
          <span class='block h-px w-10 bg-teal' aria-hidden='true'></span>
          <h1 class='label-section text-teal'>
            Posicionamiento web en Barcelona
          </h1>
        </div>

        <!-- Section heading -->
        <p
          data-animate
          style='font-family: "Titan One", cursive;'
          class='text-[clamp(1.55rem,3.1vw,2.49rem)] leading-[1.05] tracking-tight text-charcoal text-pretty mb-6'
        >
          Que te encuentren a ti antes que a ellos<span class='text-teal'>.</span>
        </p>

        <!-- Teal accent rule -->
        <div data-animate class='flex items-center mb-8' aria-hidden='true'>
          <div class='h-[3px] w-16 bg-teal rounded-full'></div>
          <div class='h-px w-24 bg-gradient-to-r from-teal/40 to-transparent'></div>
        </div>

        <p data-animate class='text-base/8 text-body text-pretty'>
          Cuando alguien busca un servicio en Barcelona, Google decide quién se lleva el cliente en segundos. Si tu negocio no aparece en la primera página, eres invisible para el <strong class='text-heading font-semibold'>90% del mercado potencial</strong>.
        </p>

        <p data-animate class='mt-4 text-base/8 text-body text-pretty'>
          Estar en la segunda página es ceder tus ventas a la competencia por falta de presencia. El posicionamiento web elimina estos bloqueos para que tu empresa sea la opción elegida.
        </p>

        <div data-animate class='mt-8'>
          <WhatsAppButton
            text='Analiza mi web'
            class='px-6 py-3 text-[0.9375rem] font-bold'
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- RIGHT: Google Local Pack screenshot -->
      <div data-animate class='mt-12 lg:mt-0'>
        <div class='serp-wrapper'>
          <Image
            src={fisioterapeutaBarcelona}
            alt='Resultados orgánicos de Google para "fisioterapeuta barcelona" mostrando las primeras posiciones'
            width={708}
            height={750}
            class='w-full h-auto block'
            loading='lazy'
          />
        </div>
        <p class='mt-3 text-center text-xs text-teal/50'>Captura real de Google · Resultados orgánicos para "fisioterapeuta barcelona"</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* ── SERP wrapper ── */
  .serp-wrapper {
    border-radius: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-default);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(52,101,109,0.08), 0 1px 3px rgba(52,101,109,0.06);
    overflow: hidden;
    background: white;
  }
</style>
